Usage: setCycleBudgetRatio [-help] {[[[{-fromTop | -fromPtn {hinst ratio}} {-toTop | -toPtn {hinst ratio}}] ] [-clock <string>]] | [-reset ]}

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
-clock <string>                   # clock name on which ratio to be applied
                                  # (string, optional)
-fromPtn {hinst ratio}            # For paths starting from partition
                                  # (string, required)
-fromTop                          # For paths starting from Top
                                  # (bool, required)
-reset                            # reset all previously declared ratio budgets
                                  # (bool, optional)
-toPtn {hinst ratio}              # For paths in partition (string, required)
-toTop                            # For paths ending in Top (bool, required)